headline: Will Walmart's $2.3 Billion Advertising Bet Work Out Better Than Jet.com?
summary: Walmart (NYSE: WMT) is one of the largest retailers in the world.  The company's recent $2.3 billion investment in Vizio is one endeavor that investors will want to monitor closely.  One of the most notable acquisitions that retailer Walmart has made in recent years was Jet.com.
